query:
SELECT 
  productId,
  partNumber,
  name,
  particleSize,
  columnLength,
  innerDiameter,
  phaseType,
  updatedAt
FROM products
WHERE brand = 'Agilent' AND prefix = 'AGIL'
ORDER BY updatedAt DESC
LIMIT 5;
